The paper deals with the behavior of graph Laplacians on manifolds with singularities and boundaries, which is a topic related to machine learning and computer vision (cs.LG, cs.CV). The paper also discusses the scaling behavior of the Laplacian operator, which is a topic in numerical analysis (cs.NA).
